Step1: generate .arp file for Arlequin
scripts: s1.scp_arp.pl, s2.generate_arp.sh
input: *.nucalign_re [nucleotide alignments of core genes, which was generated by imposing aa alignments on nuc seqs]
output: *.arp [input file for Arlequin]

Step2: run Arlequin
script: s3.run_Arlequin.sh
input: *.arp file and config file (arl_run.ars)
output: *xml [including Fst value]